### 注册
POST http://localhost:8080/api/user/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "studentId": "125001001",
  "username": "Test User",
  "password": "123456",
  "email": "125001001@link.cuhk.edu.cn",
  "phone": "13900001111"
}

### 登录
POST http://localhost:8080/api/user/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "studentId": "125001001",
  "password": "123456"
}

### 根据ID查询用户
GET http://localhost:8080/api/user/1

### 创建物品
POST http://localhost:8080/api/item
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": 1,
  "type": "lost",
  "title": "丢失蓝色背包",
  "description": "蓝色Nike背包，内有MacBook",
  "category": "背包",
  "location": "图书馆三楼",
  "lostDate": "2026-04-27"
}

### 查询物品
GET http://localhost:8080/api/item/1

### 查询列表
GET http://localhost:8080/api/item/list?type=lost&page=1&size=10

### 提交认领（user 3 认领 item 1）
POST http://localhost:8080/api/claim
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "itemId": 1,
  "userId": 3,
  "message": "这个钱包是我的，里面有我的学生证"
}

### 查看某物品的所有认领
GET http://localhost:8080/api/item/1

### 审批通过
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/claim/10/status?status=approved